reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Started out fine…broke very quickly
reviews.reviewText: This set came with 30 headphones of multiple colors, and I liked the cushion of the ear pieces. Unfortunately, within a month of use, most of these that I have checked out to kids in my classroom have lost sound in one or both sides of the headphones, or the sound has deteriorated. The kids say it sounds robotic. Of the 20 that I put in my classroom, maybe 10 of them have sound that still work. Disappointed and will not repurchase.
